    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mortifera</strong> is a single-player psychological horror game that plunges you into an investigation of the mysterious misfortune that has devastated your family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/37728e284bd48624681221512cc2834c.poster.avif?t=1741822198\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/37728e284bd48624681221512cc2834c.webm?t=1741822198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/37728e284bd48624681221512cc2834c.mp4?t=1741822198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock doors, collect objects, and use them wherever they are needed to uncover the truth.. Face the centuries-old evil lurking in the depths of the house. and the ominous, shadowy forest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/d5d30555f5fed0d07a570396d9f12338.poster.avif?t=1741822198\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/d5d30555f5fed0d07a570396d9f12338.webm?t=1741822198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/d5d30555f5fed0d07a570396d9f12338.mp4?t=1741822198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the dark corridors and forest, your only aid is a flashlight and the guiding signs that point the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/1786f831fd67d8db44ee6e13459ed83c.poster.avif?t=1741822198\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/1786f831fd67d8db44ee6e13459ed83c.webm?t=1741822198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/1786f831fd67d8db44ee6e13459ed83c.mp4?t=1741822198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore various locations in the forest to collect crucial clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/2c5a15c5518a9fbd68e25966a8232f38.poster.avif?t=1741822198\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/2c5a15c5518a9fbd68e25966a8232f38.webm?t=1741822198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/2c5a15c5518a9fbd68e25966a8232f38.mp4?t=1741822198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the tension and fear as you delve deeper into the mystery. At the same time, immerse yourself further in the game by reading or listening to notes left behind by your family and following the unfolding story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/674f6ad244571384add08ab6da079e46.poster.avif?t=1741822198\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/674f6ad244571384add08ab6da079e46.webm?t=1741822198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/674f6ad244571384add08ab6da079e46.mp4?t=1741822198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With realistic graphics and immersive sounds, paired with a minimal user interface, Mortifera keeps you on edge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/e0f35deefa82612752a63761c244aa6d.poster.avif?t=1741822198\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/e0f35deefa82612752a63761c244aa6d.webm?t=1741822198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/e0f35deefa82612752a63761c244aa6d.mp4?t=1741822198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developed by a team of two, the game draws inspiration from classic horror titles known for their psychological elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/9381aa97edbe5714bda71438d2fe1045.poster.avif?t=1741822198\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/9381aa97edbe5714bda71438d2fe1045.webm?t=1741822198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/9381aa97edbe5714bda71438d2fe1045.mp4?t=1741822198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
